Just a hint - a transhumanist may be considered a new breed of a Renaiisance
person, combining reasonable understanding of the world with active
social position and interest in personal development, on the best levels
allowed by the modern civilization, and attempting to draw coherent connections
between them.


Also, you can look at transhumanist websites that explore all these issues
in sufficient detail.



